Title: AIM- 9X Product Development                                                                                                     32.673      27.132       37.939
Description: Continuation of Primary Hardware Development/Pre-Planned Product Improvement (technical refresh) efforts
for the AIM-9X weapon system. This includes systems engineering and program management, as well as support required
to ensure AIM-9X missile integration with US military aircraft platforms. This also includes efforts to redesign Block II missile
components to mitigate obsolescence, ensure producibility and increase reliability. It will incorporate anti-tamper and cyber
security technology improvements, and address hardware and software improvements to facilitate follow-on capability. In addition,
the program will evaluate and begin risk reduction efforts that will address hardware and software improvements to facilitate
follow-on capability and mitigate obsolescence.

