                                                                                                                   FY 2024    FY 2025      Base        OOC        Total
and AN/SPN-35 Block II to new SPN-XX Brizo Landing System; purchase of remaining development system
material. Includes preliminary testing of Brizo Landing system subsystems.
FY 2026 Base Plans:
Previous planned efforts (e.g. Critical Design Review (CDR), SIL updates and continued development of AN/
