D. Acquisition Strategy
AN/TPX-42 Voice/Video recorder replacement, Joint Precision Approach and Landing System Interface, Shipboard trainer, and Air Traffic Control (ATC) Console are all
in progress ECPs, with improvements being incorporated into the production of AN/SYY-1(V) upgrade kits.

 AN/SPN-50 replacement program is an ACAT IVT program. All other projects are non-ACAT upgrades to existing systems. An evolutionary acquisition approach
 is being used to introduce these technology advancements that either satisfy user requirements, such as all weather operation, or address supportability and cost of
 ownership problems.




