dynamics, adjudication capabilities, together with models and algorithms to support realistic, interactive
information warfare exercises.
- Complete new low-profile and reduced weight and power aperture with simultaneous transmit and receive
signals compatible with multiple satellite constellations.
- Initiate force-on-force unscripted experimentation of AI-augmented Command and Control (C2) systems for
"one versus many" swarm control in small unit (company and below) simulated combat scenarios.
- Initiate experimentation of AI-enabled tactical advisors that analyze sparse data to provide small unit
commanders with sound tactical recommendations in Expeditionary Advanced Base Operations (EABO) support
scenarios.
- Initiate multi-modal simulation of operations in the information environment to develop realistic data for
information warfare.
