A. Mission Description and Budget Item Justification
This Program Element supports the advanced development and demonstration of technologies to improve warfighter performance, safety and survivability. Naval
investment in these areas is essential in order to improve the ability to enhance, maintain, and sustain Warfighter effectiveness.

